</li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-item-link js-clickTrack" href="/ct/our-latest/" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav" data-label="Our Latest">Our Latest</a></li><li class="nav-item js-menuTrigger"><a class="nav-item-link js-clickTrack" href="/ct/archives/" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav" data-label="The Magazine">The Magazine</a><div class="nav-dropdown js-menuDropDown display-none"><div class="inner-content p-relative ml-auto mr-auto"><img width="15" height="7" class="caret caret4mag" src="/ct/channel/img/icon_triangle-lg.png" /><div class="subnav-top uppercase align-items-center d-flex"><ul class="nav subnav d-flex"><li class="subnav-item"><a href="https://subscribe.christianitytoday.com/servlet/OrdersGateway?cds_mag_code=TDY&cds_page_id=182695&cds_from_id=ctsubmenu_drpdwn_sub" class="js-clickTrack" data-category="Sub Link" data-action="Christianity Today" data-label="Screwtape’s Practical Advice for Dealing with the Present">Subscribe</a></li><li class="subnav-item"><a href="/ct/member-benefits/" class="js-clickTrack" data-category="Sub Link" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Member Benefits">Member Benefits</a></li><li class="subnav-item"><a href="https://subscribe.christianitytoday.com/servlet/OrdersGateway?cds_mag_code=TDY&cds_page_id=182696&cds_from_id=ctsubmenu_drpdwn_gift" class="js-clickTrack" data-category="Sub Link" data-action="Christianity Today" data-label="Screwtape’s Practical Advice for Dealing with the Present">Give a Gift</a></li></ul></div>
