</span></div><div class="meta-container " itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><h2 class="title article-title" itemprop="name">
					Screwtape’s Practical Advice for Dealing with the Present
					
				</h2><div class="deck spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-15" itemprop="description">What C. S. Lewis’s senior devil would recommend in response to COVID-19.</div>
<div class="article-byline "><span itemprop="author">Gary S. Selby</span><span class="pipe"></span><span class="postdate" itemprop="datePublished">March 26, 2020</span></div>
<h2 class="title spacer-top-10"></h2></div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="article-featured-image "><div class="container"><figure class="p-relative align-center spacer-top-40"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/116320.jpg?w=940" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/116320.jpg?w=1880 2x" width="940" alt="Screwtape’s Practical Advice for Dealing with the Present" title="Screwtape’s Practical Advice for Dealing with the Present" /></figure><figcaption class="spacer-top-5 spacer-bottom-5"><div class="credit ">
									Image:
									
										Illustration by Mallory Rentsch / Source Images: Pedro Lastra / CDC / Unsplash / Run Studio / Getty Images
									</div>
</figcaption></div></section><section class="container"><div class="spacer-top-25 u-cf social-nav-item"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/system/social/styles/share.css?07082014"></link>
				<div
					class="ctSocialShare ctSocialShare_horizontal ctSocialShare_fallback"
					style="display: none; visibility: hidden; opacity: 0"
